@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_soilbp(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = ((wp.cos(tmp + 0.24) / (v1 + 0.70 * v0 + 0.53)) + (wp.cos(v0 + 0.05) / v1))
    v1 = (0.26 - v1)
    v2 = (wp.cos((v1 + 0.99 * v0 + 0.43)) * v2)
    tmp = ((wp.cos(v2 + 0.23) / 0.88) - ((v0 + 0.67 - v2 + 0.96) * (v1 + 0.81 - v0 + 0.92)))
    data[tid] = v0
